title: Dream Theater Discography 1986 - 2013
description:
Dream Theater Discography 1986 - 2013


I hope there's no need to introduce Dream Theater
 <a href="
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dream_Theater" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dream_Theater</a>


Recently I lost my copy of their "The Score" DVD... No need to be worried - I said to myself... it will be easy to be found online.
It wasn't... I had to struggle on some obscure cyberlocker to have it.
I've always taken for granted that the best rock band in activity was widely available in torrents.
But, apart a good torrent with their studio albums, there was no extensive discography...

So now you have it...
It includes their new 2013 eponimous album leaked a week before the official release date (and at first listening I can say it's really good :) ). 

We start since the Majesty epoch until today, including bootlegs, live, and demos and all the singles I was able to recover.

There are 60 albums and 10 singles and this should be satisfying even for the captive fans.

All the album are zipped (since the number of files was too high for TPB).

The sampling rate is 320kbps.


Enjoy :)
